Task 5: Template Literal Output Program Requirements ● Create variables to store: ○ name (string) ○ role (string) ○ organization or company name (string) ● Use template literals to generate a formatted introduction message.


//PROGRAM

let personName = "PETCHIAMMAL MURUGAN";
let role = "Web Developer";
let company = "Codem Inc";

let message = `Hello, my name is ${personName}. I work as a ${role} at ${company}.`;

console.log(message);


//Output

Hello, my name is PETCHIAMMAL MURUGAN. I work as a Web Developer at Codem Inc.
